cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this repository, please cite it. Philosophia is an open research
  programme and is not a peer-reviewed publication.
title: "Philosophia: can experience be made from derivable worlds?"
abstract: >-
  A preregistered research programme testing whether algebraic and geometric
  worlds can provide primary experience to small models trained from scratch,
  and whether the resulting structure reduces future work and transfers across
  worlds and representations.
